---
title: Buffalo Chicken Ranch Wraps with Mixed Greens & Cheddar Cheese
description: Spicy buffalo sauce and cooling ranch dressing are a match made in heaven! For this speedy wrap, chicken is tossed in buttery Frank’s hot sauce, then rolled up in tortillas with mixed greens, cheddar cheese, and buttermilk ranch. Spicy, tangy, creamy, and quick—it’s all your wildest lunch dreams come true.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buffalo-chicken-ranch-wraps-6e309421.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/buffalo-chicken-ranch-wraps-62a79216086f5a15940ed264-8c11f132.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/buffalo-chicken-ranch-wraps-62a79216086f5a15940ed264
author: HelloFresh
time required: 10 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 700 kcal
  fat: 42 g
